995b32ac-5d7f-49c8-b22f-a8a4e2504ca0.name: Student charge creation
995b32ac-5d7f-49c8-b22f-a8a4e2504ca0.description: Administrative departments can request the creation of a charge for a student to the Bursar’s office, such as to charge fees related with Registration, Meals, Tuitions, and Housing. After a request is submitted, the Bursar’s office can approve or cancel the request. If approved, the student receives an email with new charge details.
